## 八、业务模型常用方法

### 通用查询

```php
// 获取单条（不存在返回空模型）
$card = MiniCardScore::mk()->where(['card_code' => $code])->findOrEmpty();

// 检查是否存在
if (!$card->isExists()) {
    // 不存在
}

// 统计数量
$count = MiniCardScore::mk()->where(['batch_no' => $batchNo])->count();

// 列表
$list = MiniCardScore::mk()->where(['status' => 1])->select()->toArray();

// 获取某字段值
$score = MiniCardScore::mk()->where(['id' => $id])->value('score');
```

### 静态方法示例（卡密检查）

```php
/**
 * 检查卡密是否可以使用
 * @param int $cardType 卡密类型
 * @param string $cardCode 卡密码
 * @param int $userId 用户ID
 * @return array ['can' => bool, 'reason' => string]
 */
public static function canUseCard(int $cardType, string $cardCode, int $userId): array
{
    $card = MiniCardScore::mk()->where(['card_code' => $cardCode])->findOrEmpty();

    if (!$card->isExists()) {
        return ['can' => false, 'reason' => '卡密不存在！'];
    }
    if (intval($card->status) !== 1) {
        return ['can' => false, 'reason' => '卡密已被禁用！'];
    }
    if ($cardType === self::TYPE_VIP && $card->expire_time > 0 && $card->expire_time < time()) {
        return ['can' => false, 'reason' => '卡密已过期！'];
    }
    // ... 更多检查
    return ['can' => true, 'reason' => ''];
}
```
